Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving the fierce \Nbattle at the Fish-Man Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigating the treacherous Maubeugemour Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they met a Giant girl named Lily \Nwho ate the Mini-Mini Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got fired up to help \Nher save her father -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panz Fry from the Navy's ship. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a mysterious group called the \NNeo Navy was trying to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surface and finish them off at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're responsible for all \Nthe raids on pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:04:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am! I'm gonna cut \Nthis guy's head off too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a three-way battle heated up between the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hats, the Navy and the Neo Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worthless pirates are no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they were able to bring down \Nthe menacing enemy - Shuzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this was just the first foray into \Nthe New World for the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:05:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:14.04,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Arriving! A Burning Island - Punk Hazard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa! Are we gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The volcano's erupting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the needles point to that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Wait"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! There is a volcano! It looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the 3 needles is \Npointing at the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too peculiar even \Nin the strange New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's erupting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right there! Who \Ncares about the needles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! We can't get any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the sea is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's the Giant \NShellfish Panz Fry gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could cook \Nthis in that sea of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Now isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sparks!\N--The ship will catch fire too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny is super not gonna let us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with this sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those fish bones, bones, bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you just call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this? The \NTransponder Snail is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?! You have a stomachache?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! That's an emergency signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pick it up, can we hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than 50 percent of \Nemergency signals are fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a Navy trap - one they use often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the line is tapped, they \Nwill find out where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, you have to be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? My name is Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You picked up too fast and said too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold... Is this the Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not the Boss. Is it cold there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My colleagues are getting \Ncut one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai are gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, what's your name?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got killed - of course there is trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody just cut him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he was acting and it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How level-headed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of samurai, Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what you think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's that name of the swordsmen \Nfrom the Wano Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wano Kingdom - closed \Noff to the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even affiliated \Nwith the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say those swordsmen \Ncalled samurai are so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even the Navy can't approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This great sword - Shusui was once \Ncarried by a legendary samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become its owner, \Nthe sword will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let this samurai's \Nbody... take the beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of that country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said Punk Hazard, \Nnot the Wano Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he mean the island of fire right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was using a Baby Transponder Snail,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's about how far the signal can reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go help that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, think again! I think it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, what's your name?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody please help me! I'm on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say Punk Hazard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they have gotten there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle at the Fish-Man Island, \Nthe incident after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we plot the course they took from there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk Hazard... It's possible they're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever you ask me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get charred!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you guys! Stop bullying pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi! Let's head for Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Smoker-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk Hazard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been deserted since they sealed it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,off after what happened 4 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be anybody there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think any living thing \Ncan live there now but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'd make sense to go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are setting out for Punk Hazard, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Vice Admiral Smoker, \Nit's a restricted area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me about the law, you scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who's going to the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there is uncertainty, \Nwe shouldn't all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky, I need the Mini-Merry!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Are you gonna go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let you go by yourself, you'll \Ndisappear without telling us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, he needs some company but \Nnot the random belly-warmer guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?! \NI'll cut you, kinky cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Company? I'll go with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe we'll pass \Non this one. Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll draw straws. No complaints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain! I'll go even if I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! If I'm picked, go instead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say "Good luck lies in odd numbers"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stake all my life on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#%=/+$!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, his companions are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won? How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I made a special \NGiant Shellfish lunch box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milky Road!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! You created a path of clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw the same thing at the Sky Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's made of clouds, you \Nhave to take it while it's stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, recon team! Here we go, Mini-Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll have a chance to go later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take care!\N--Usopp, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Giant Shellfish is yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating your lunch already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're going over the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get across the sea of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these clouds gonna be \Nhere when we come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that it stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's a nice day to scout an island!\N--But it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, do those clouds reach the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if they don't, \NLuffy will find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san's so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I didn't get picked to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But letting him go by \Nhimself wasn't an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll come back as soon as \Nthey find out there's no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you planned it out so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you a cold dessert \Nwith the Giant Shellfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys want it too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there is the erupting island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you there should be an entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, maybe somebody \Nwas living here in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one can live here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The emergency signal earlier must \Nhave come from somewhere far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't look good but I like the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are eating lunch too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna eat yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy, do you want this one?\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an excellent cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun outdid himself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The disorder I had 2 years ago is recurring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys, the truth is, I have \Na Fear-of-unknown-islands-osis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got a headache all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a tightness in my chest too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a stomachache!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:05.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNK HAZARD ISLAND ENTRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's beach the Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the emergency \Nsignal came from inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like no one's allowed \Nto enter this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Danger" "Keep out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are marks of the World \NGovernment and the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means even if somebody's here, \Nhe belongs to the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wasted trip! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Zoro, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, it's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Trespassing is a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we pirates are criminals anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep me out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna challenge the Government?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we already did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hot, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't seem like the \Nisland has been burning forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So was there a disaster? Or an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were probably not people's houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there were some kind \Nof Government facilities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shut this island \Ndown because it started
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,burning and became dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or these facilities were \Nhazardous from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that the Log Pose didn't \Npoint to this island troubles me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy from earlier - are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call them! They're murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now you have an appetite?\N--It's stress eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man on the Snail said \N"It's cold," didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold... Is this the Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really hot here but he said it was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, Sherlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a cold place on this burning island?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that he had a chilling experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, you're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that noise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yummy, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna melt in the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cooling me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, I feel a sharp pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are my teeth sensitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys only get to eat it \Nbecause there are leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there are a lot for you, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just noticed there's something strange \Nabout the sky above the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The far side looks like the Arctic sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's bigger than a Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was the noise of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:22:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Does it actually exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a mythical creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that it's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at those features...
